OL,6,FThree people who died in a motorbike
OL,7,Fcrash in the Scottish Borders have
OL,8,Fbeen named.
OL,10,FAndrew Lartey, 29, and Georgia Tate,
OL,11,F23, both from Newcastle, and Jason
OL,12,FGibbon, 37, from Northumberland, died
OL,13,Fin the collision on the A6088 on
OL,14,FSunday 28 July.
OL,16,FMr Gibbon was riding his Suzuki GSXR
OL,17,Fbetween Bonchester Bridge and Carter
OL,18,FBar when he was involved in the
OL,19,Fcollision with Mr Lartey's Kawasaki
OL,20,FZX1400 motorbike.
