OL,6,FMs Tate was a pillion passenger on the
OL,7,FKawasaki bike.
OL,9,FIn a statement, the families of Mr
OL,10,FLartey and Ms Tate said: "We are
OL,11,Fdevastated by the loss of Georgia and
OL,12,FAndrew, they will be sorely missed by
OL,13,Fall who knew them.
OL,15,F"We ask for our privacy to be
OL,16,Frespected at this difficult time."
