OL,6,FAnd paying tribute to Mr Gibbon, his
OL,7,Ffamily said: "We are devastated of the
OL,8,Floss of a much loved son, brother,
OL,9,Funcle, boyfriend and devoted friend to
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,12,F"He will be greatly, sadly missed. We
OL,13,Fare comforted by the messages from
OL,14,Fmany. We would like to ask for privacy
OL,15,Fto allow the family to grieve at this
OL,16,Fvery difficult time."
OL,18,FSergeant Barry Sommerville, of Police
OL,19,FScotland, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,20,Fwith the family and friends of the
OL,21,Fthree people who died.
